Title: mongodb_cluster: Monitoring of cluster balance and size
Level: 1
Component: checks
Compatible: incomp
Edition: cre
Version: 2.0.0i1
Date: 1566804879
Class: feature

New check to monitor cluster relevant parameters: Balance of chunks, number of jumbo chunks, status of balancer.

For using this new feature, you have to re-deploy the agent with the new mongodb plugin.
